import React from 'react'
import { Segment } from 'semantic-ui-react'

const SegmentExampleSegments = () => (
  <Segment.Group>
    <Segment>Top</Segment>
    <Segment>Middle</Segment>
    <Segment>Middle</Segment>
    <Segment>Middle</Segment>
    <Segment>Bottom</Segment>
  </Segment.Group>
)

export default SegmentExampleSegments
